---
alwaysApply: true
---

GitHub hygiene:
- Never mention "Cursor", "cloud agent", or similar tooling in commit messages, PR titles, PR descriptions, or any other GitHub-visible text.
- Write commits and PRs as if a human teammate authored them.

Workflow:
- Before starting any work, run `git fetch origin` and pull the latest code from the default branch.
- Assume the workspace may be stale; never assume it is up to date.
